<h5><strong>When do we collect information?</strong></h5>
  <ul>Information is collected every minute for anyone who has linked their BYOC seat to their steam account.</ul>

<h5><strong>How do we use your information?</strong></h5>
  <ul>Your information is used to populate the server list to help users find games being played by others in the BYOC.</ul>

<h5><strong>Where do we save your information?</strong></h5>
  <ul>Information is stored in a secure data center in the USA. </ul>

<h5><strong>Your Consent</strong></h5>
  <ul>Either of the following ways will stop your information from being collected:
  <ul>
    <li>Change your <%= link_to "Steam Profile Privacy", "https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=4113-YUDH-6401", :target => '_blank' %> to friends only, or private.</li>
    <li><%= link_to "Sign in through Steam", "/auth/steam" %> and navigate to your byoc.ninja settings page.<br /> Change "Display game information" to no, and save.</li></ul>
  </ul>

